Key Match Events: Axar Patel is Player of the Match
Post-Match Reflections: Rohit Sharma: 'It's very satisfying to win this game. We worked really hard as a unit to come through this stage and to win this game like that was a great effort from everybody.'
Jos Buttler: 'India outplayed us. We let them get 20-25 runs too many on a challenging surface. They outplayed us and deserved the win.'
Axar Patel: 'I’ve bowled many over in the past in the power play. I knew the wicket was stopping so I didn’t try too many things.'
Miscellaneous Highlights: India will face South Africa in the T20 World Cup final
The match was played on a challenging surface
Others: India have won all the games that were completed with one washout in the initial group stage
